<p>Normally held on the first Thursday of each month, at 20:00 in the Village Hall meeting room, although a meeting is not normally held in August.  The actual day may be changed to ensure the committee is quorate.<br />
Please check the home page to confirm the actual meeting date and time.</p>
<h4 id="annual-general-meetings">Annual General Meetings</h4>
<p>Our AGM is normally held in June.</p>

